{"tid":2219649,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"自製clotted cream","createTime":"2020-09-27T04:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T09:53:36.000Z","uid":105798,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8f9908a2a3b77ea1fb92d19dc98f89eb349ba9bb","tid":2219649,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:42:10.000Z","msg":"目標:<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.biggerbolderbaking.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Clotted-Cream-Thumbnail.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.biggerbolderbaking.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2FClotted-Cream-Thumbnail.jpg&h=93169e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁小弟就買咗一大樽heavy cream<br />\n放入焗爐170F 低溫焗12個鐘<br />\n冇錯你冇睇錯<br />\n係12個鐘<br />\n同埋個溫度range 好窄<br />\n太熱會焦糖化(第一次去到最尾先發現太熱)<br />\n所以都買咗個焗爐用溫度計<br />\n<br />\n12個鐘後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QeAkeVn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQeAkeVn.jpg&h=d7b258dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後要放入雪櫃多12個鐘<br />\n之前若果反起個面<br />\n就會發現表面個層係固體<br />\n下面仲係液體<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0WW0eVZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0WW0eVZ.jpg&h=1878211c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁我就通常直接倒走d 水佢<br />\n<br />\n點食?<br />\n搵舊scone, 放pat clotted cream 上去<br />\n再擺pat jam<br />\n示意圖: <br />\n<img src=\"https://images.eatsmarter.com/sites/default/files/styles/max_size/public/scones-with-raspberry-jam-and-clotted-cream-584688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.eatsmarter.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fmax_size%2Fpublic%2Fscones-with-raspberry-jam-and-clotted-cream-584688.jpg&h=7a349180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真實: (唔好理後面個兩塊肉)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0K5q2U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0K5q2U.jpg&h=76d93fd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nref: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LDyyAb6lB48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLDyyAb6lB48&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0kzob1WjLKDnR9IVaUJYWuI%3D&h=504dcaf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LDyyAb6lB48</a>"},{"pid":"7f48a974ef6dcf55be9d6198fadab3b1d219051c","tid":2219649,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:46:18.000Z","msg":"12個鐘咪好哂電<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb7036d9590fb32be3569f93aaad6230b49e901","tid":2219649,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f48a974ef6dcf55be9d6198fadab3b1d219051c","tid":2219649,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:46:18.000Z","msg":"12個鐘咪好哂電<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:48:10.000Z","msg":"焗爐應該係on--&gt;off--&gt;on--&gt;off 咁玩法?<br />\n見唔夠熱先開陣之類<br />\nbtw 170F = 80C 所以其實唔係太熱<br />\n同埋我係用gas oven"},{"pid":"ddc9a4149348d2a728e196c25a83c2a3c601c5cb","tid":2219649,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:31:25.000Z","msg":"巴打好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d6561fe229aae00b8ed954addc5913d64bab76","tid":2219649,"uid":299794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"配scone真係好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d7f4aee108cbd22c00f6db87ba7c8738cd3e6b","tid":2219649,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7d6561fe229aae00b8ed954addc5913d64bab76","tid":2219649,"uid":299794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"配scone真係好撚好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:39:48.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr